(13, 'Mt everest', 'Everest base camp and kala pat', 110500, '<h2 style=\"text-align: start;\"><font color=\"#202124\" face=\"courier new\" size=\"5\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b style=\"\">12 days</b></span></font></h2><div><font color=\"#202124\" face=\"courier new\" size=\"5\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b style=\"\"><br></b></span></font></div><div><div class=\"p-intro w-box t\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: none; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0px 0px 35px; position: relative; padding: 0px; border-top: none; color: rgb(42, 52, 57); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: start;\"><div class=\"top-details scrl\" id=\"overview\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"top-row t-hlghts\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px; position: relative;\"><strong class=\"h-title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 22px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: block; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-transform: uppercase;\">HIGHLIGHTS</strong><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding: 0px 0px 10px 27px;\"><span class=\"icon-check-mark\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 4px; color: rgb(62, 179, 104); font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span>Get close up, panoramic views of the world s highest mountains from Kalapatthar</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding: 0px 0px 10px 27px;\"><span class=\"icon-check-mark\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: a