; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(222, 45, 45); position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 4px; font-size: 7px; border: 1px solid rgb(222, 45, 45); padding: 5px 0px 0px 1px; border-radius: 50%; width: 18px; height: 18px; text-align: center; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span>Rescue and medical assistance if needed</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding: 0px 0px 7px 30px;\"><span class=\"icon-cross97\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(222, 45, 45); position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 4px; font-size: 7px; border: 1px solid rgb(222, 45, 45); padding: 5px 0px 0px 1px; border-radius: 50%; width: 18px; height: 18px; text-align: center; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span>Services not mentioned in the Included section or set as optional</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding: 0px 0px 7px 30px;\"><span class=\"icon-cross97\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(222, 45, 45); position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 4px; font-size: 7px; border: 1px solid rgb(222, 45, 45); padding: 5px 0px 0px 1px; border-radius: 50%; width: 18px; height: 18px; text-align: center; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span>Porter to carry your bag during the trek</li></ul></div></div>', 'package2.jpg'),
(14, 'Mt everest', 'Everest Helicopter Tour Packag', 710000, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.35pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;mso-outline-level:2\"><span style=\"font-size: 20pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;;\">Everest\r\nHelicopter Tour Package Highlights<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.35pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">The Everest Base Camp Helicopter Tour to EBC is a perfect way to\r\nexplore and enjoy a close-up view of awe-inspiring natural beauty, culture, and\r\nmighty mountains in a very short period of time.&nbsp;<strong>Everest Base Camp Helicopter tour</strong>&nbsp;offers\r\nthe best aerial view of the massive Mount Everest and other several peaks in\r\nthe Khumbu region.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.35pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">This exciting helicopter tour lets you fly high over the lush\r\nhills and alpine forests of rhododendron with awesome views of the chain of\r\nmountains in the Himalayas. Everest Base Camp Helicopter tour can be idyllic\r\nfor those adventure lovers who wish to gain an adrenaline rush and an\r\nadventurous experience.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.35pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Mount Everest (8848 meters) is the highest peak in the world. It\r\nis the dream destination for many people to see and explore Mount Everest. Even\r\nif some people have a great desire to visit Everest, they may not be\r\ncomfortable with walking through the entire trekking route. Others may be\r\nlimited by time or any health issues. This Everest Base Camp Heli tour is the\r\nperfect option for them too.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.35pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Mount Everest Base Camp Helicopter Tour is an excellent addition\r\nto the entire tour package for individuals in Nepal. Although it only takes a\r\nfew hours, you can get all the way from Kathmandu to Mount Everest and back.\r\nThis is one of the best alternatives to the&nbsp;<strong>Everest Base Camp Trek</strong>,\r\nespecially for those who are limited by time.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.35pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;mso-outline-level:2\"><span style=\"font-size: 20pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Beautiful\r\n     Aerial view of rhododendron and pine forests and lush valleys, villages,\r\n     lakes, and rivers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Experience\r\n     the most spectacular aerial view of turquoise lakes, rivers, icefall,\r\n     glaciers, beautiful snowcapped hills, and Sherpa villages flying over the\r\n     famous Sagarmatha National park which is also listed asa UNESCO world\r\n     heritage site.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Experience\r\n     the spectacular views of majestic mountains, and picturesque scenery and\r\n     feel the soul of the Khumbu region in no time.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Sit on the\r\n     lap of the world’s highest peak Mount Everest and experience the\r\n     unparalleled beauty of nature it offers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Spectacular\r\n     360-degree views of awe-inspiring mountains like Kangtega, Kusum,\r\n     Thameserkhu, Kangaru, Lhotse, Ama Dablam, Pumori, Nuptse, Cho Oyu,\r\n     Tawache, Cholatse, Island Peak, Pumori, Lobuche, Mera Peak, and the Mount\r\n     Everest.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Experience\r\n     the exciting landing at the world’s high altitude viewpoint Kalapatthar\r\n     (5,644.5 m (18,519 ft.)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:NE\">Enjoy\r\n     Delicious Breakfast with a 360-degree view of majestic mountains in\r\n     Everest View Hotel, The highest place hotel in the world at 13000ft.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n     11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-bidi-language:NE\">100 %&nbsp;Full Refund&nbsp;guarantee if no flight\r\n     made due to bad weather</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-bidi-language:NE\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background: rgb(251, 254, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:\r\nNE\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:#FBFEFF\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"548\" style=\"width:411.25pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:\r\n solid #DDDDDD .75pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;border-left:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;\r\n  border-bottom:none;border-right:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;\r\n  mso-border-left-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;background:#F9F9F9;padding:6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.55pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Charter Cost<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;border-left:none;\r\n  border-bottom:none;border-right:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;\r\n  mso-border-right-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;background:#F9F9F9;padding:6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.55pt;text-align:justify;\r\n  line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">N\r\n  Rs </span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n  color:#202124;background:white\">552,000</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;border-right:none;\r\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;\r\n  mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;padding:6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.55pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Cost for Group Joining<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;border-left:none;mso-border-top-alt:\r\n  solid #DDDDDD .75pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;mso-border-right-alt:\r\n  solid #DDDDDD .75pt;padding:6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt 6.7pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.55pt;text-align:justify;\r\n  line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">N\r\n  Rs </span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n  color:#202124;background:white\">158,000</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>', 'package3.jpg');
