(15, 'Mt everest', 'Everest Base Camp (EBC) Hiking', 221372, '<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:solid #E5E7EB 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\nsolid #E5E7EB .25pt;padding:0in 0in 0in 0in\">\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;padding:0in;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Description<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Mount Everest</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">(8,848m)</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> is a\r\nlegendary mountain. And while reaching its summit is the goal of many people, I\r\nbelieve hiking to its famed</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\"> base camp</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> is an\r\nadventure all on its own.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Over the course of </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">16 days</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">, you\r\nwill have the chance to hike through beautiful </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Himalayan</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> terrain.\r\nThere is so much to see during this trek that every day will be worthwhile.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">The trek will start in the city\r\nof</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\"> Kathmandu</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">, where you will arrive, and also\r\nhave a day to tour the city. Afterwards, we will take an exciting flight to </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Lukla</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">. And\r\nfrom there, the trekking will begin.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">With </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Everest</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;looming\r\nabove and beyond, constantly staring down, awaiting your arrival, you will see\r\nsome truly amazing things. Some of the best sights include </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Namche Bazaar</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">, several\r\n</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Sherpa villages</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">,&nbsp;and the </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Pangboche</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> and </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Thyangboche monastaries</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">We will be at high altitude\r\nthroughout the trek, but there will be several stays designated for </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">acclimatization</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">.\r\nHowever, the advantage of the altitude will be the incomparable views you will\r\nhave. You will have the chance to marvel at a </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">panoramic view</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> of </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Everest</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> from </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Kala Pattar.</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;And\r\nyou will also have the chance, throughout the hike, to admire some of the\r\nhighest mountains in the world, from </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Lhotse (8,516m)</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> to </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Nuptse (7,861m)</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">.\r\nFinally, at the culmination of our trek, we will reach the famous </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Everest Base Camp (5,362m)</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Everything about Everest is\r\nmagical. That includes its base camp. And considering the altitude of that camp\r\nis higher than such famous mountains as the Matterhorn (4,478m) and Mont Blanc\r\n(4,810m) it iss easy to why. So please message me if trekking to this amazing\r\narea interests you.</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">If you have more time in </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Nepal</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">, and\r\nwant to trek to another great mountain, I also offer a </span><a href=\"https://www.explore-share.com/trip/kanchenjunga-29-day-guided-trek/\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;border:solid #E5E7EB 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;padding:0in\">29 day trip</span></b></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> to the\r\nbase camp of </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; border: 1pt solid rgb(229, 231, 235); padding: 0in;\">Kanchenjunga (8,586m)</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Show less<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:solid #E5E7EB 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\nsolid #E5E7EB .25pt;padding:0in 0in 0in 0in\">\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid #E5E7EB .25pt;\r\npadding:0in;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\"><span style=\"font-family: Aria